imdb.plot outline: Kids who love fire trucks and fire fighting heroes will love these amazing non-stop fire truck action videos. This Award-winning, "Lots and Lots of" fire truck series brings you racing red fire engines, giant pumper trucks, hook n' ladders, rescue rigs, super soakers, a firehouse trip, fire safety tips, fire fighters putting out fires, and more. Fun to watch and sing-along to music by James Coffey.
